{
  "texts": [
    "This indicates that other LLMs, especially RAG chatbots, should receive more attention from researchers in the future.",
    "ConclusionTo conclude, this literature review collected and summarized the research results of studies in recent years that focused on the application of LLMs in EFL speaking or writing education.",
    "These studies demonstrated the strength of LLMs in interaction activities but also showed their defects of slight inaccuracy.",
    "Generally, they depict an optimistic prospect of integrating them into many aspects of English language education.",
    "The quality of accessibility would enable LLMs to become a strong tool to assist EFL learners' self-study on speaking, and the relaxed and meaningful conversation created by IPAs can eliminate EFL learners' anxiety effectively."
  ]
}